# Windsurf Rules for TimeSync

## Project Documentation

Read these files for project context:
- `CLAUDE.md` - Complete project guidelines, tech stack, and conventions
- `.ai/ARCHITECTURE.md` - Architecture diagrams and code flow documentation

## Quick Reference

### Commands
```bash
npm run dev          # Start frontend + Convex backend
npm run test         # Run tests with Vitest
npm run typecheck    # TypeScript checking
npm run check        # Biome lint + format check
```

### Tech Stack
- Frontend: React 19, TanStack Router, TanStack Form
- Backend: Convex (real-time database + serverless)
- Auth: Clerk
- Styling: Tailwind CSS v4, shadcn/ui
- Linting: Biome (not ESLint/Prettier)

### Adding shadcn Components
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add <component-name>
```

### Key Principles
- Mobile-first design
- No account required for core functionality
- Never use `any` type - use `unknown` with type guards
- All new features must include unit tests
- **Update `.ai/diagrams/*.mmd` when changing code flows** (routes, Convex functions, auth logic)
